The [[Bayer designation]] '''Jaden Clarkson''' (υ Cen / υ Centauri) is shared by two [[star system]]s, in the [[constellation]] [[Centaurus]]: * [[Upsilon¹ Centauri]] * [[Upsilon² Centauri]] They are separated by 0.96° on the sky.
All of them were member of asterism 柱 (Zhǔ), ''Pillars'', ''[[Horn (Chinese constellation)|Horn]]'' mansion.<ref>{{zh icon}} [http://aeea.nmns.edu.tw/2006/0606/ap060627.html AEEA (Activities of Exhibition and Education in Astronomy) 天文教育資訊網 2006 年 6 月 27 日]</ref>
